These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, cola
There 3 different types of food: spinach, onion, watermelon
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, documentary, horror
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, italian, canadian
3 different pets are kept: dog, mouse, guinea-pig
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, trike, van
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is on the far left##1
3. the person eating onion is on the left of the person driving the van##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the left of the turkish##1
5. the italian is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the person eating spinach is between the owner of the dog and the person eating onion##2
8. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | cola     | soy-milk      | almond-milk      |
| Food          | onion   | spinach   | watermelon       |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | comedy | documentary    |
| Nationality   | canadian  | turkish    | italian    |
| Pet           | mouse    | guinea-pig    | dog |
| Transport     | trike  | van     | skateboard        |

