.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, hot-chocolate, juice
There 3 different types of food: apple, cherry, broccoli
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, animation, horror
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, canadian, american
3 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, turtle
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, swimming, handball
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person eating apple##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person eating broccoli is between the american and the person drinking juice##2
7. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching horror movies and the owner of the turtle##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate     | sprite        | juice      |
| Food          | cherry    | broccoli       | apple  |
| Movie-Genre   | horror     | animation | romance    |
| Nationality   | american | indian   | canadian    |
| Pet           | hamster      | ferret  | turtle      |
| Sport         | handball    | swimming      | climbing |

