.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, carrot, lime
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, chess, card-games
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, hip-hop, pop
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, polish, american
3 different pets are kept: mouse, lizard, bird
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, taxi, skateboard
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the american and the owner of the mouse##2
2. the polish is on the left of the turkish##1
3. the turkish is the turkish##1
4. the owner of the bird is the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the polish is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person eating lettuce##2
7. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
8. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person eating lime##1
9. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | lettuce  | carrot    | lime   |
| Hobby         | cooking | card-games | chess |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | hip-hop    | salsa |
| Nationality   | american    | polish  | turkish  |
| Pet           | lizard     | bird   | mouse       |
| Transport     | taxi | ship     | skateboard       |

