6. the indian is on the right of the american##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
8. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person eating peach and the person driving the skateboard##2
9. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3       |
